    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## 2. 數據清洗與群組定義\n",
        "## (Data Cleaning and Group Definitions)\n",
        "\n",
        "**中文說明：**\n",
        "為了確保雙樣本推論的準確性，我們首先剔除這兩個核心變數中的缺失值（NaN）。接著，我們依據重新編碼後的邏輯將資料明確劃分為兩組：**Group 1 悲傷組**（代碼為 1）與 **Group 2 不悲傷組**（代碼為 0）。\n",
        "\n",
        "**English Description:**\n",
        "To ensure the accuracy of our two-sample inference, we first filter out any missing values (NaN) within these two core variables. Subsequently, we clearly partition the dataset into two distinct comparison groups based on the recoded logic: **Group 1 (Sad Group)** represented by code 1, and **Group 2 (Non-Sad Group)** represented by code 0."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "yVrb6eB12dFn"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# 移除缺失值，確保統計檢定準確\n",
        "df_clean = df.dropna(subset=[sad_col, smoke_col])\n",
        "\n",
        "# 分別切出：Group 1 悲傷組 (1) 與 Group 2 不悲傷組 (0)\n",
        "group_sad = df_clean[df_clean[sad_col] == 1]\n",
        "group_nosad = df_clean[df_clean[sad_col] == 0]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"缺失值處理完畢，已將資料分類為兩大群組。\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "aG0yom4s2vOe",
        "outputId": "c7ab5e47-b2ab-4113-9a6b-07191d162288"
      },
      "execution_count": 7,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "缺失值處理完畢，已將資料分類為兩大群組。\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## 3. 獨立任務 1：計算基本群組摘要\n",
        "## (Independent Task 1: Computing Basic Group Summaries)\n",
        "\n",
        "**中文說明：**\n",
        "我們需要分別計算出「悲傷組」（Group 1）與「不悲傷組」（Group 2）各自的有效總人數 ($n_1, n_2$)、實際吸菸人數 ($x_1, x_2$) 以及各自的樣本吸菸比例 ($\\hat{p}_1, \\hat{p}_2$)，並計算出兩組比例的實際差異大小，作為後續雙樣本比例 Z 檢定的基礎。\n",
        "\n",
        "**English Description:**\n",
        "We need to calculate the total effective sample size ($n_1, n_2$), the number of smokers ($x_1, x_2$), and the sample smoking proportions ($\\hat{p}_1, \\hat{p}_2$) for the \"Sad Group\" (Group 1) and the \"Non-Sad Group\" (Group 2) respectively. We also compute the observed difference between the two proportions to lay the foundation for the subsequent Two-Proportion Z-Test."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "uIZiwfau2wc0"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# 計算 Group 1 (悲傷組) 的數據\n",
        "n1 = len(group_sad)\n",
        "x1 = group_sad[smoke_col].sum()\n",
        "p1_hat = x1 / n1\n",
        "\n",
        "# 計算 Group 2 (不悲傷組) 的數據\n",
        "n2 = len(group_nosad)\n",
        "x2 = group_nosad[smoke_col].sum()\n",
        "p2_hat = x2 / n2\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"Group 1 (悲傷組): 總人數(n1) = {n1}, 吸菸人數(x1) = {x1}, 吸菸比例(p1_hat) = {p1_hat:.4f}\")\n",
        "print(f\"Group 2 (不編傷組): 總人數(n2) = {n2}, 吸菸人數(x2) = {x2}, 吸菸比例(p2_hat) = {p2_hat:.4f}\")\n",
        "print(f\"兩組吸菸比例實際差異 (p1_hat - p2_hat) = {(p1_hat - p2_hat):.4f}\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "ghnkxy4b3LJD",
        "outputId": "384b28af-ec0d-4aa9-cd8d-b0ef0d7d8f16"
      },
      "execution_count": 8,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Group 1 (悲傷組): 總人數(n1) = 3854, 吸菸人數(x1) = 1064, 吸菸比例(p1_hat) = 0.2761\n",
            "Group 2 (不編傷組): 總人數(n2) = 9320, 吸菸人數(x2) = 1508, 吸菸比例(p2_hat) = 0.1618\n",
            "兩組吸菸比例實際差異 (p1_hat - p2_hat) = 0.1143\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## 4. 獨立任務 2 & 3：執行雙樣本比例 Z 檢定與信賴區間計算\n",
        "## (Independent Task 2 & 3: Two-Proportion Z-Test and Confidence Interval)\n",
        "\n",
        "**中文說明：**\n",
        "本階段進入統計推論核心。我們執行雙樣本比例 Z 檢定（Two-Proportion Z-Test），藉由產出的 Z 檢定統計量與 P 值，推論「感到悲傷或絕望」是否與「目前吸菸狀況」存在顯著的關聯性。同時，我們手動建構兩組比例差異的 95% 信賴區間，用以評估母體比例差異的可能範圍。\n",
        "\n",
        "**English Description:**\n",
        "This stage enters the core of statistical inference. We perform a Two-Proportion Z-Test to obtain the Z-test statistic and P-value, which helps deduce whether \"feeling sad or hopeless\" is significantly associated with \"current smoking status.\" Simultaneously, we construct a 95% Confidence Interval (CI) for the difference between the two proportions to evaluate the plausible range of the true population difference."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ZObKjDgB4nxd"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "from statsmodels.stats.proportion import proportions_ztest\n",
        "\n",
        "# 1. 執行 Two-proportion Z-test\n",
        "# count 傳入兩組的吸菸人數 [x1, x2]，nobs 傳入兩組的總人數 [n1, n2]\n",
        "z_stat, p_value = proportions_ztest(count=[x1, x2], nobs=[n1, n2], alternative='two-sided')\n",
        "\n",
        "# 2. 計算兩組比例差異的 95% 信賴區間\n",
        "prop_diff = p1_hat - p2_hat\n",
        "se_diff = np.sqrt(p1_hat * (1 - p1_hat) / n1 + p2_hat * (1 - p2_hat) / n2)\n",
        "ci_lower = prop_diff - 1.96 * se_diff\n",
        "ci_upper = prop_diff + 1.96 * se_diff\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"Z 檢定統計量 (Z-statistic): {z_stat:.4f}\")\n",
        "print(f\"P 值 (P-value): {p_value}\")\n",
        "print(f\"兩組吸菸比例差異 (p1_hat - p2_hat): {prop_diff:.4f}\")\n",
        "print(f\"兩組比例差異的 95% 信賴區間 (95% CI for Difference): [{ci_lower:.4f}, {ci_upper:.4f}]\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "sqAjL4gI4zX9",
        "outputId": "618e59ed-f529-4fce-9adf-2e7e5815d038"
      },
      "execution_count": 9,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Z 檢定統計量 (Z-statistic): 15.0536\n",
            "P 值 (P-value): 3.2674477555382817e-51\n",
            "兩組吸菸比例差異 (p1_hat - p2_hat): 0.1143\n",
            "兩組比例差異的 95% 信賴區間 (95% CI for Difference): [0.0983, 0.1302]\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## 5. 獨立任務 4：產出與匯出核心統計總結表\n",
        "## (Independent Task 4: Generating and Exporting the Core Summary Table)\n",
        "\n",
        "**中文說明：**\n",
        "為了符合專案規範的 Cookiecutter 架構標準，我們將上述計算出的所有關鍵描述統計與推論指標（包含樣本數、成功次數、比例、Z值、P值與信賴區間）整合進一個結構清晰的 DataFrame 中，並將此總結表自動匯出儲存為 `outputs/tables/summary_table.csv`。\n",
        "\n",
        "**English Description:**\n",
        "To comply with the Cookiecutter project structure standards, we consolidate all the computed key descriptive and inferential metrics (including sample sizes, successes, proportions, Z-statistic, P-value, and confidence intervals) into a well-structured DataFrame. This summary table is then automatically exported and saved as `outputs/tables/summary_table.csv`."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "cE1AQRO67TBr"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "\n",
        "# 1. 建立結構化字典\n",
        "summary_data = {\n",
        "    'Metric (指標)': [\n",
        "        'Group 1 (Sad) Sample Size (n1)',\n",
        "        'Group 1 (Sad) Smokers (x1)',\n",
        "        'Group 1 (Sad) Proportion (p1_hat)',\n",
        "        'Group 2 (Non-Sad) Sample Size (n2)',\n",
        "        'Group 2 (Non-Sad) Smokers (x2)',\n",
        "        'Group 2 (Non-Sad) Proportion (p2_hat)',\n",
        "        'Difference in Proportions (p1_hat - p2_hat)',\n",
        "        'Z-test Statistic',\n",
        "        'P-value',\n",
        "        '95% CI Lower Bound',\n",
        "        '95% CI Upper Bound'\n",
        "    ],\n",
        "    'Value (數值)': [\n",
        "        n1, x1, round(p1_hat, 4),\n",
        "        n2, x2, round(p2_hat, 4),\n",
        "        round(prop_diff, 4),\n",
        "        round(z_stat, 4),\n",
        "        p_value, # P-value 保持精確度\n",
        "        round(ci_lower, 4),\n",
        "        round(ci_upper, 4)\n",
        "    ]\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "# 2. 轉為 DataFrame\n",
        "summary_df = pd.DataFrame(summary_data)\n",
        "\n",
        "# 3. 自動建立 Cookiecutter 架構資料夾並匯出 CSV\n",
        "os.makedirs('outputs/tables', exist_ok=True)\n",
        "summary_df.to_csv('outputs/tables/summary_table.csv', index=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"🎉 總結表已成功匯出至 'outputs/tables/summary_table.csv'！\")\n",
        "summary_df"
      ],
